comments: Irina is a great teacher! She sets clear and concise goals, and she is super professional. Just do the homework, study it, and tests are not hard. Her comments are very helpful too; she knows the material very well. The hardest thing about tests, for me, was time. It really killed me on the final. Make sure you know the subject and perform quickly.

The homework assignments will take hours, don\'t procrasturbate. Tests are rough, study hard. BELIEVE
